Package: xmms2-mlib-updater
Architecture: any
Depends: xmms2-core (= ${Source-Version}), libxmms2client (= ${Source-Version}), libxmms2client-glib (= ${Source-Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: XMMS2 - Medialib Updater
 This client provides File Alteration monitoring. To keep your medialib up to
 date.
